install steps
-install imageio 
	pip install imageio
	pip install cv2
-download ffmpeg
	run down.py

run steps
-create directory "vids" besides video.py and convert
-put videos in the directory "vids"
-add executable permission if required
	chmod +x convert
-run the conversion
	./convert
-a folder will be created having all folders of frames of the videos 


